### Create contact type - B2B Client
# Note: First create "Industry" custom field, then use its MongoDB _id here
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "B2B Client",
  "description": "Business-to-business customers",
  "fields": [
    { "id": "sys_name", "required": true },
    { "id": "sys_email", "required": true }
  ]
}

#### Create contact type - Individual Customer
#### Note: Use MongoDB _id from your custom "Preferred Contact Method" field
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Individual Customer",
  "description": "Direct consumers",
  "fields": [
    { "id": "sys_name", "required": true },
    { "id": "695a4573d9b1b90a9aa12d4a", "required": false }
  ]
}

### Get all contact types
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Get single contact type by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types/695a75ce0885b07cee3cd33a
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Update contact type
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types/695cb1fca841a890b8d75bdb
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description for contact type",
  "fields": [
    { "id": "sys_name", "required": true }
  ]
}

### Delete contact type (cascades to contacts)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types/695a75ce0885b07cee3cd33a
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Error - Create type with non-existent field (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Type",
  "description": "Will fail",
  "fields": [
    { "id": "nonexistent_field", "required": true }
  ]
}

### Error - Duplicate name (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/contact-types
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "B2B Client",
  "description": "Duplicate name",
  "fields": [
    { "id": "sys_email", "required": true }
  ]
}
